---
const title = "About Us | FinanceHub - Expert Financial Accuracy";
const description = "Learn about the mission of FinanceHub and the professional expertise behind our 50+ financial calculators.";
---

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1e3a8a;
            --secondary: #2563eb;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-light: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
        }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #f8fafc; color: var(--text-dark); margin: 0; padding: 0; line-height: 1.8; }
        
        header { background: white; padding: 25px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
        .logo span { color: var(--secondary); }

        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        
        .about-card { background: white; padding: 50px; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border); box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
        h1 { color: var(--primary); font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h2 { color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-top: 30px; border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary); padding-left: 15px; }
        
        .profile-box { background: #f0f9ff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 30px 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
        .profile-info h4 { margin: 0; color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .profile-info p { margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-light); }

        .mission-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .mission-item { background: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .mission-item strong { color: var(--primary); display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 60px; }
        .back-home { display: inline-block; margin-top: 30px; color: var(--secondary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <a href="/" class="logo">Finance<span>Hub</span></a>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="about-card">
            <h1>Our Story & Mission</h1>
            <p>Welcome to <strong>FinanceHub</strong>, a premium destination for precise financial calculations. In an era of complex global markets, we believe that clarity and accuracy should be accessible to everyone—from individual investors in the UK to business owners in the USA and Canada.</p>

            <div class="profile-box">
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <h4>Md Merajul Islam</h4>
                    <p>Founder & Lead Auditor | Internal Audit Professional</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Why FinanceHub?</h2>
            <p>Most online calculators provide generic results. At FinanceHub, we integrate <strong>Audit-Level Precision</strong> into every tool. Developed by a professional in Internal Audit & Cost Control, our algorithms are cross-verified with international accounting standards to ensure you never make a decision based on a rounding error.</p>

            <div class="mission-grid">
                <div class="mission-item">
                    <strong>100% Data Privacy</strong>
                    Calculations are processed locally; we never store your financial data.
                </div>
                <div class="mission-item">
                    <strong>Global Standards</strong>
                    Tools optimized for USA, UK, Canada, and European tax & loan models.
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Our Expertise</h2>
            <p>FinanceHub features over 50+ dedicated tools covering:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Loan & Mortgage Amortization (Reducing Balance)</li>
                <li>Investment ROI & Compound Interest Tracking</li>
                <li>Business Profit Margin & Break-even Analysis</li>
                <li>VAT, GST, and International Tax Calculations</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Our goal is to reach <strong>1,000+ calculators</strong>, making this the most comprehensive financial toolkit on the web. Thank you for trusting us with your numbers.</p>
            
            <a href="/" class="back-home">← Explore All Calculators</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 FinanceHub Pro. Verified by Internal Audit Experts.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
